FixtureType.Description: Lumipix 15IP is a tour-ready LED pixel batten conceived to be fully versatile and perform outdoor, delivering advanced brightness and colour mixing by offering individual pixel control of each cell. The robust die-cast aluminium structure with omega quick lock socket on the bracket and the waterproof power and signal connector make Lumipix 15IP suitable for the most demanding environments.
